

PORTLAND GLOBAL ADVISORS, LLC: Overview of Firm




















Overview of Firm
Portland Global Advisors, LLC is a closely held wealth management firm based in Portland, Maine.  We primarily manage and oversee global investment portfolios for a select number of high net worth families and individuals.  In addition to our management and oversight responsibilities, we are actively engaged in all aspects of our clients' financial lives including helping clients meet their lifestyle, philanthropic and estate planning goals.
Portland Global Advisors, LLC is registered as an investment adviser with the SEC.










