PORTLAND GLOBAL ADVISORS, LLC: Working with Us






















    
    
      A typical course of events before we embark on a relationship is to meet with the potential client to discuss their particular financial situation and for us to understand their goals and expectations. Initial consultations are complimentary and require no commitment.
      
      When you become a client of Portland Global Advisors, we work together with you to develop an individualized asset allocation plan taking into account tax, estate, and other considerations. This plan is dynamic and should change as your situation changes. We often work as part of a team which may include tax, legal and other outside advisors. 
      
      On an on-going basis, clients receive a quarterly statement from us detailing holdings and the performance of those holdings. Clients also receive our quarterly market analysis "The Portland Global Advisor."
      
      Finally, we are always available to review and answer questions about any aspect of a clients financial situation.

    
    

























