Portland Global Advisors LLC Buys Celgene Corp, Sells Mobileye NV, The Kroger Co


July 11, 2017, 06:38:01 PM EDT
By insider, GuruFocus









































Shutterstock photo


Portland Global Advisors LLCNew Purchases: CELG ,Added Positions: SPY , EFA , MDY, VSS, EEM, IWM, VWO, IBM, BK, SLB,Reduced Positions:VTI, ABT, DVY, BMY, GILD, IRM, JNJ, MAN, DVMT, F,Sold Out:MBLY, KR,For the details of Portland Global Advisors LLC's stock buys and sells, go to http://www.gurufocus.com/StockBuy.php?GuruName=Portland+Global+Advisors+LLCThese are the top 5 holdings of Portland Global Advisors LLCSPDR S&P 500 ( SPY ) - 194,458 shares, 18.85% of the total portfolio. Shares added by 1.72%SPDR MidCap Trust Series I ( MDY ) - 101,878 shares, 12.97% of the total portfolio. Shares added by 1.44%iShares MSCI EAFE ( EFA ) - 265,060 shares, 6.93% of the total portfolio. Shares added by 3.78%Vanguard Total Stock Market ( VTI ) - 94,535 shares, 4.72% of the total portfolio. Shares reduced by 1.13%Vanguard FTSE Emerging Markets ( VWO ) - 240,082 shares, 3.93% of the total portfolio. Shares added by 1.88%New Purchase: Celgene Corp (CELG)Portland Global Advisors LLC initiated holdings in Celgene Corp. The purchase prices were between $114.41 and $134.31, with an estimated average price of $122.44. The stock is now traded at around $132.25. The impact to the portfolio due to this purchase was 0.08%. The holdings were 1,578 shares as of 2017-06-30.Sold Out: Mobileye NV (MBLY)Portland Global Advisors LLC sold out the holdings in Mobileye NV. The sale prices were between $61.25 and $62.99, with an estimated average price of $62.Sold Out: The Kroger Co (KR)Portland Global Advisors LLC sold out the holdings in The Kroger Co. The sale prices were between $22.29 and $30.78, with an estimated average price of $28.47.Warning! GuruFocus has detected 3 Warning Signs with CELG. Click here to check it out.CELG 15-Year Financial DataThe intrinsic value of CELGPeter Lynch Chart of CELGPremium MembersThis article first appeared on GuruFocus .



